snippet.title: G.I JOE: WRATH OF COBRA | Console Reveal Date| indie.io
snippet.description:
G.I JOE: WRATH OF COBRA is coming to Nintendo Switch, PlayStation 5 and Xbox X|S Series on November 21, 2024!!

Cobra returns once again with its most fiendish plot yet and it's up to G.I. JOE to defeat them once more! Pick one of the real American heroes, gear up, and get straight into the fight in this retro side-scrolling beat 'em up!

G.I. JOE and all related characters are trademarks of Hasbro and are used with permission. © 2024 Hasbro. All Rights Reserved. Licensed by Hasbro.

Available Now on Steam
